abilities.effect:
If the target is within 6" of this unit, the target is **gazing into eternity** until the start of your next turn. Otherwise, roll a dice. On a 3+, the target is **gazing into eternity** until the start of your next turn.&#x20;

While the target is **gazing into eternity**, it must end all moves no further from this unit than it was at the start of the move and it cannot be removed from the battlefield by an ability that would allow it to be set up again on the battlefield.&#x20;

**Designer’s Note:** *This includes pile-in moves.*

For the rest of the phase, the following effects apply:&#x20;

• This unit's combat attacks that target that enemy unit have **Crit (2 Hits)** and score critical hits on unmodified hit roll of 5+.

• If the target is destroyed by this unit's combat attacks this phase, add 1 to the Attacks characteristic of melee weapons used by other friendly **HEDONITES OF SLAANESH DAEMON** units while they are wholly within 12" of and visible to this unit.&#x20;

battleTraits.effect:
If the unit using this ability is a **PARAGON**, pick 1 of the effects below. Otherwise, your opponent must pick 1 of the effects below.&#x20;

***Succumb***: For the rest of the turn, when the target is using a **CHARGE** ability, it must end that charge move no further from the **HERO** using this ability.

***Resist***: For the rest of the turn, subtract 2 from charge rolls for the target.
